The invention discloses a computer online survey evidence-taking and analysis system and a method, relating to the field of network security and providing evidence for maintaining the network security. The system comprises a data acquisition module, a data extraction module, a process supervision module and a data storage module, wherein the data acquisition module is used for acquiring needed data from a host; the data extraction module is used for carrying out digital notarization on the acquired data; the process supervision module is used for recording operation information in the online evidence-taking process; and the data storage module is used for storing the digitally-notarized data which is acquired from the host. The method comprises the steps of data acquisition, data extraction, process supervision and data storage. Since the invention has an acquisition mechanism of easy-loss data and an acquisition mechanism of specific file data in storage medium of the host, and also comprises a digital notarization and whole-process supervision mechanism, therefore, the evidence-taking result has very high comprehensiveness and creditability, thus providing evidence for maintaining the network security.
